# Connection Details Template (Local Only)

Copy this file to `system/config/connections.md` and fill in local values. The real
`connections.md` is gitignored because it contains machine addresses, channel IDs,
and other local operator details.

## Purpose

This file is a local bridge card for Spirit-in-Cursor/Anvil. It answers: "From
this workstation, how do I reach Turtle and the relevant practice surfaces?"

It is not Turtle's runtime source of truth. Runtime topology belongs in
`~/turtleos/mage_registry.yaml`.

## Configuration Precedence

1. `~/turtleos/mage_registry.yaml` — canonical Turtle runtime topology.
2. `system/config/connections.md` — local operator reference for this workstation.
3. `TURTLE_SPEC.md` and lore — public pattern, with no secrets.

